                        <p class="text-gray-400 line-clamp-3 mb-4">Exploring the latest trends and technologies shaping the future of web development and design. From AI-powered tools to WebAssembly and beyond.</p>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                            <span>May 15, 2025</span>
                            <span>Bhoumish Grover</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
                
                <!-- Blog Card 2 - Design -->
                <a href="blog-post.html" class="group block bg-gray-900/50 rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover border border-gray-800 hover:border-accent-rose transition-all duration-300">
